Underfoot, the rubber outsole is fitted with ASICS Trusstic System, good for midfoot support and stability.

story: The Gallery Dept. x ASICS Gel 1130 ‘Oyster Grey’ delivers Josue Thomas’ understated interpretation of the lifestyle runner. story: The HAL STUDIOS x ASICS Gel 1130 ‘Forest’ presents the second installment of the partner brands’ collaborative series. Inspired by Japan’s lush forests, as well as the Shinto shrines found within them, the lifestyle runner features an airy green mesh upper with tonal shaggy suede detailing on the toe cap and signature side stripes. Leather overlays in off-white and brown tones add to the shoe’s earthy palette, while a co-branded sockliner in a vibrant orange finish delivers a contrasting pop of color. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an off-white foam midsole with a visible GEL insert in the heel.

story: The Comme Des Garçons SHIRT x ASICS Vic NBD ‘White’ treats the low-profile silhouette to a blank-slate makeover. ASICS Gel-Quantum Zientzia Kiko Kostadinov Dark Grey Blue
story: The Kiko Kostadinov x ASICS Gel Quantum Zientzia 'ISS' debuts a new silhouette conceived in partnership with the London-based menswear designer. A product of the ASICS Institute of Sport Science (ISS) in Japan, the lifestyle runner sports a breathable dark grey mesh upper with tonal synthetic overlays and shiny metallic silver accents. Contrasting pops of royal blue appear on the interior lining and signature side stripes. Built with FF BLAST foam, the midsole is enhanced with ASICS’ scutoid GEL technology, featuring a unique 3D geometry for improved shock absorption.

ASICS Gel-Lyte III Remastered Ronnie Fieg Super Yellow
story: The Ronnie Fieg x ASICS Gel Lyte 3 Remastered ‘Super Yellow’ delivers the Kith founder’s premium take on the lifestyle runner. Built to the exact specifications of the duo’s inaugural 2007 collaboration, the retro silhouette sports a grey nubuck upper with perforated detailing on the toe box and quarter panel. The latter is accented with tonal netting and signature tiger stripes in a bright yellow hue. ‘Fieg’ is embroidered on the split tongue, while dual ASICS and Kith branding decorates the sockliner. The sneaker rests on a full-length EVA midsole with ASICS Gel cushioning.
